{"id": "1405532264233697280", "channel_id": "1405532264233697280", "type": 0, "author_id": "1356970554027933877", "author_name": "calmdreab", "author_bot": false, "content": "私人約稿禁一切", "timestamp": "2025-08-14T12:43:25.320000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "1nekodrool", "emoji_id": "1206774407562006600", "count": 7}, {"emoji": "1nekowoteyes", "emoji_id": "1206774624977948717", "count": 4}, {"emoji": "1neko_lick", "emoji_id": "1200338620633063485", "count": 7}, {"emoji": "love", "emoji_id": "1356053099931897977", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "Emoji_LK_M_08", "emoji_id": "1400771650064089112", "count": 1}, {"emoji": "wow", "emoji_id": "1356053147029864518", "count": 1}], "attachments": [{"id": "1405532264573440132", "filename": "551b0e1a6ad386304d8190562f02cbb0_1755172719367.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1222411, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1405532264233697280/1405532264573440132/551b0e1a6ad386304d8190562f02cbb0_1755172719367.png?ex=69cbc16d&is=69ca6fed&hm=48f939daaec82728c61784f670357079d8d26730b3759d3742e7e228385bb1d7&"}, {"id": "1405532265269821631", "filename": "4fcee68ed110caffeed32797278c6219_1755172758962.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 1267060, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1405532264233697280/1405532265269821631/4fcee68ed110caffeed32797278c6219_1755172758962.png?ex=69cbc16d&is=69ca6fed&hm=faaea6fe33d7a1b38f7c2a5c504beed9f0cd7b54ee7714a2377e11a3f62ae8b6&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1405532264233697280", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "彌撒格最般配的男同性戀", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1395992145638330368"]}
{"id": "1405414479180595253", "channel_id": "1386311129608749076", "type": 0, "author_id": "883992032530563082", "author_name": "void_1546.", "author_bot": false, "content": "獎勵關\n\n後勤支援\n\n在你深入這片區域一段時間後，你胸口上的彌撒格校徽傳出一聲微弱的聲音，「⋯⋯嘶⋯⋯請問是XXX嗎（當前角色），目前我們仍在搜救中，您需要支援嗎？」\n選擇\n\n【我需要物資】回復30%生命值。\n\n【不用】獲得XXX的覺醒卡（當前角色）（若已有，則改為「靈感」）\n\n【請派遣人員協助】\n（朵兒：增加20點生命值上限，回復10%生命值。）\n（溫柯爾：獲得隨機一個隨機造物）\n（艾瑞卡：三選一命輪）\n隱藏選項：本次探索中見過「融毀．朵兒」\n（融毀．朵兒：扣除15點生命值上限，將一張奇怪的鑰令加入卡組）\n\n\n\n\n選擇結果\n\n【我需要物資】你接受了他的支援，平靜的音樂在你耳邊響起，讓你緊繃的精神舒緩一些。\n\n【不用】你堅韌不屈的精神疑似引來了某個存在的注目，你感覺自己好像有了什麼變化。\n\n【請派遣人員協助】你希望能與學院其他的人員交流，他沉默一會後讓你選擇要與誰交流，你選擇⋯⋯\n\n\n【朵兒】增加20點生命值上限，回復10%生命值。\n\n【溫柯爾】獲得隨機一個隨機造物。\n\n【艾瑞卡】三選一命輪。\n\n隱藏選項：本次探索中見過「熔燬．朵兒」\n【熔燬．朵兒】扣除15點生命值上限，將一張奇怪的鑰令加入卡組。\n\n選擇結果\n\n【朵兒】希望你不會讓我失望，已經沒有多餘的時間可以浪費了。\n\n【溫柯爾】嗚嗚嗚，這裡還是太黑暗了，不行不行不行不行！\n\n【艾瑞卡】正在武器檔案中查詢兵器⋯⋯結果為：「3」。\n\n隱藏選項：本次探索中見過「熔燬．朵兒」\n【熔燬．朵兒】這些「小玩具」就送給你了，能與終末相近，何嘗不是一種解脫？", "timestamp": "2025-08-14T04:55:23.175000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1386311129608749076", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Slay the Spire Morimens Mod Text Provided Post", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811", "1182359790249332756"]}
{"id": "1405414548814692484", "channel_id": "1386311129608749076", "type": 19, "author_id": "883992032530563082", "author_name": "void_1546.", "author_bot": false, "content": "Logistical support\nAfter lingering in this area for a short while, the Mythag badge on your chest vibrates faintly, carrying a voice laced with static.\n“…bzzzz… can you hear me? Is this XXX (current character)? We’re still searching for the other academy members… do you need assistance?”\nOptions\n\n【Request Supplies】Restore 30% HP.\n【Reject】Gain XXX’s Rouse Card (Current Character). If already owned, receive “Insight” instead.\n【Please dispatch personnel for assistance】\n(Doll: Increases maximum health by 20 points and restores 10% HP.)\n (Winkle: Obtains a random relic.)\n (Erica: Choose one of three Wheel of Destiny.)\nHidden Option: Seen \"（Doll:lnferno\" during this exploration. ）\n（“Doll:lnferno”: Deducts 15 points from maximum health and strange posse joins the deck.)\n\nChoices result\n\n【I Need Supplies】You accepted his support, and calm music played softly at your ears, soothing your tense spirit.\n\n【Reject】Your indomitable spirit seems to have attracted the attention of a certain being, and you feel as if something has changed within you.\n\n【Please dispatch personnel for assistance】You hope to communicate with other people in the academy. He is silent for a moment and then asks you to choose who you want to communicate with. You choose…\n\n\nChoices result\n\n【Doll】I hope you won't let me down, there's no time to waste.\n \n【Winkle】Woo woo woo, it’s still too dark in here, no no no no!\n\n【Erica】Searching for weapons in the weapons archive... Result: \"3\".\n\n【Doll:lnferno】These 'little toys' are given to you. Isn't it a relief to be near the end?", "timestamp": "2025-08-14T04:55:39.777000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1405414479180595253", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1386311129608749076", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Slay the Spire Morimens Mod Text Provided Post", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359914895646811", "1182359790249332756"]}
